#: ../../talk/bots.rst:2
msgid "Bots and commands"
msgstr "Botanna agus orduithe"

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:5
msgid "Bots"
msgstr "Botanna"

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:7
msgid ""
"Bots can respond to chat messages, provide automated replies, and integrate "
"with external services. Your administrator can enable bots for your Talk "
"instance."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le botaí freagra a thabhairt ar theachtaireachtaí comhrá, freagraí"
" uathoibrithe a sholáthar, agus comhtháthú le seirbhísí seachtracha. Is "
"féidir le do riarthóir botaí a chumasú do d’eispéireas Talk."

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:9
msgid "Some examples of available bots:"
msgstr "Seo roinnt samplaí de na róbait atá ar fáil:"

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Call summary** — Posts an overview message after a call ends, listing all "
"participants and outlining any tasks that were mentioned."
msgstr ""
"**Achoimre ar an nglao** — Foilsítear teachtaireacht forbhreathnaithe tar "
"éis dheireadh an ghlao, ina liostaítear na rannpháirtithe uile agus ina "
"leagtar amach aon tascanna a luadh."

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Agenda bot** — Helps manage meeting agendas with time monitoring and "
"permission-based access control."
msgstr ""
"**Bot cláir oibre** — Cabhraíonn sé le cláir oibre cruinnithe a bhainistiú "
"le monatóireacht ama agus rialú rochtana bunaithe ar cheadanna."

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:13
msgid "**Roll a dice** — Type ``/roll`` in a conversation to roll dice."
msgstr ""
"**Caith dísle** — Clóscríobh ``/roll`` i gcomhrá chun dísle a chaitheamh."

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:15
msgid ""
"A full list of available bots and installation instructions can be found in "
"the `Talk administration documentation <https://nextcloud-"
"talk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/bot-list/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir liosta iomlán de na róbait atá ar fáil agus treoracha suiteála a "
"fháil i `ndoiciméadacht riaracháin Talk <https://nextcloud-"
"talk.readthedocs.io/en/latest/bot-list/>`_."

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:18
msgid "Commands"
msgstr "Orduithe"

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:21
msgid "Commands have been removed in favor of Bots."
msgstr "Baineadh orduithe i bhfabhar na mBot."

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:23
msgid ""
"Nextcloud allows users to execute actions using commands. A command "
"typically looks like:"
msgstr ""
"Ligeann Nextcloud d’úsáideoirí gníomhartha a fhorghníomhú ag baint úsáide as"
" orduithe. De ghnáth bíonn ordú mar seo a leanas:"

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:25
msgid "``/wiki airplanes``"
msgstr "``/vicí eitleáin``"

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:27
msgid ""
"Administrators can configure, enable and disable commands. Users can use the"
" ``help`` command to find out what commands are available."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le riarthóirí orduithe a chumrú, a chumasú agus a dhíchumasú. Is "
"féidir le húsáideoirí an t-ordú ``cabhair`` a úsáid chun a fháil amach cé na"
" horduithe atá ar fáil."

#: ../../talk/bots.rst:29
msgid "``/help``"
msgstr "``/cabhair``"
